title: Napoleon (XXX/SD/WEB-RIP)
description: Starring: Lea Martini, Erika Bella, Erica Bella, Maria Bellucci The story of Napoleon in any language results in the same–a small man with illusions of grandeur who uses any means necessary to acquire power and victory. In this case, Napoleon uses sex as a strategy to gain power over the females he wishes to conquer. Initially skirmishes indicate that Napoleon may have finally found a successful strategy as he marches across a continent–to pillage, plunder and ravish the lovely wenches along the way. 1:04:23 https://www.imageuploads.co.uk/image/esacd https://www.imageuploads.co.uk/image/esgOe https://www.imageuploads.co.uk/image/esfiE
